"Transfer to a bowl and place in fridge for 15 minutes to chill. Clean and dry mixing bowl."},{"isHeader":true,"content":"Horseradish Créme"},{"content":"Place yoghurt and horseradish in mixing bowl then combine <b>10 sec\/speed 3<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula, then mix <b>5 sec\/speed 3<b>."},{"content":"Serve gazpacho chilled, topped with horseradish créme and a sprinkle of chives."}],"hintsAndTricks":["Refer to <i>The Basic Cookbook<\/i> for the vegetable stock paste recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","1h 40m","4 portions"]}